title: 297I.25 INFORMATION RETURNS.
text:
To the extent licensed agents or brokers are utilized in accordance with section 60E.12, they shall report to the commissioner the premiums received for direct business for risks resident or located within this state which the licensees have placed with or on behalf of a risk retention group not chartered in this state.
MS 2018 [Repealed, 1Sp2019 c 6 art 21 s 4]
